Interface GuiReprCollectionTable.TableTargetCell

  • All Superinterfaces:
    GuiReprCollectionTable.TableTarget
    All Known Implementing Classes:

    GuiReprCollectionTable
    public static interface GuiReprCollectionTable.TableTargetCell
extends GuiReprCollectionTable.TableTarget
    a sub-type of table-target, also supporting selecting partial columns; in the type, GuiReprCollectionTable.TableTarget.getSelectedCells() returns the values of the partial columns. it also supports obtaining all-cells in a row.
